      "RealLives enhances the compass's transformative competencies, as learners need to innovate (create new value), solve dilemmas (reconcile tensions and dilemmas), and make informed and ethical decisions (take responsibility) within their simulated lives. The platform fosters global understanding, a key area of knowledge, skills, attitudes, and values in the compass, by providing learners with a real-world perspective on global issues.",
