    title:
      'The Transformative Impact of RealLives on Gunseo School: A Journey Towards Global Citizenship and Empathy',
    excerpt:
      'How Gunseo Global School used RealLives to strengthen global citizenship, empathy, literacy, and student-led social innovation.',
    category: 'School Spotlight',
    tags: ['Global Citizenship', 'Empathy', 'School Innovation'],
    author: 'Parag Mankeekar',
    authorRole:
      "Co-Founder @ RealLives Foundation | RealLives Simulation, Edupreneur, 'Games for Good & Changemaking' advocator",
    authorAvatar:
      'https://d2jn82ki4w4ftn.cloudfront.net/reallives-website/common-newsletter-page/ceo-image.jpg',
    publishedOn: 'June 17, 2024',
