      'Davidson, C. N., & Goldberg, D. T. (2022). The new digital learning: Neural adaptations in Gen Z and Alpha. Harvard Education Press.',
      'Deloitte Global Education Survey. (2024). Future of learning: Generational perspectives on education. Deloitte Insights.',
      'de Oliveira Andreotti, V. (2011). (Towards) decoloniality and diversality in global citizenship education. Globalisation, Societies and Education, 9(3-4), 381-397.',
