    title:
      'From Data to Lived Meaning: How RealLives Simulation Enables Deep Empathy and Action-Oriented SDG Learning in Classrooms',
    excerpt:
      'How Human Ecology Research (2025) validates RealLives as a data-driven, empathy-rich pathway for agency-centered SDG learning.',
