      'RealLives does not remove hope. It removes illusion.',
      'It does not tell young players what to believe. It shows them that lives unfold differently depending on circumstances.',
      'This understanding does not weaken empathy. It deepens it.',
      'Why This Matters for Those Who Support It',
      'Global challenges rarely persist because of lack of information.',
      'They persist because of lack of understanding across lived realities.',
      'RealLives addresses this gap not by persuasion, but by exposure.',
